messages.messageBody:
Nancy, Hope you are up and running soon.
Kelli T
Dnowens@... wrote:Our computer crashed, and is beyond repair. So untill the money is there for
a new computer, I won't be online anytime soon. I accessed my account with my
dh's computer at work, but I doubt he wants me there everyday, reading all my
mail. <g> I hope to come back soon! I will really miss everyone of you. Take
care.
~Nancy

Our computer crashed, and is beyond repair. So untill the money is there for
a new computer, I won't be online anytime soon. I accessed my account with my
dh's computer at work, but I doubt he wants me there everyday, reading all my
mail. <g> I hope to come back soon! I will really miss everyone of you. Take
care.
~Nancy
